<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued February 12 at 8:48PM EST until February 13 at 7:00PM EST by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 PM EST
SUNDAY...
* WHAT...Lake effect snow. Additional snow accumulations of up
to 1 inch tonight, and 2 to 4 inches on Sunday.
* WHERE...Berrien County. The greatest additional snowfall
amounts are expected on Sunday across northern Berrien County.
* WHEN...Until 7 PM EST Sunday.
* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions.
* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Wind chills will drop to around zero
tonight and again on Sunday night.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.</instruction>
